{"tid":1802484,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"教定你民陣如何回應1月1遊行有參加者大叫香港獨立","createTime":"2019-12-29T13:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T13:46:56.000Z","uid":23949,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4732bbadb48e9a227c6729733006b7880edcffda","tid":1802484,"uid":23949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:25:51.000Z","msg":"係政府一直唔聽民意<br />\n錯失所有回應時機<br />\n當初103萬人遊行上街叫你撒回<br />\n你唔聽<br />\n逼到而家有五大訴求<br />\n講左半年五大訴求你唔理<br />\n先逼到市民追求香港獨立<br />\n民陣只係一個申請社會行動搞手<br />\n我地無能力去要求所有參加者去擁護或者唔擁護邊一套思想<br />\n我地只能夠一直與民同行 爭取公義<br />\n林鄭 請你立即回應五大訢求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"974bcfac8928e91b3fd2bf22e23c89ba279a2be9","tid":1802484,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:26:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國聯署有三份  呢家<span style=\"color: red;\">仲有一份未達標</span><br />\n而且差好遠呀<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 9xxx/50000</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK99HbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=655c77bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9aea06c5628a8994a88d3e6ccbb8d1eab568c0d9","tid":1802484,"uid":23949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:27:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HdZRiiJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHdZRiiJ.jpg&h=7ae5fd3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3ee9c06e7c2d385ccd4a20f506a7d1dd8c8f8d0","tid":1802484,"uid":127067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T13:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji